{"tid":2432211,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"舒適堡搞優惠","createTime":"2021-03-04T06:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T10:12:26.000Z","uid":381174,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c711c7a297842334b6051353e30d7861b224f8a1","tid":2432211,"uid":381174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:55:01.000Z","msg":"有冇人join左 聽聞一千蚊一年"},{"pid":"27c3bd6baa87ba3a4da0e0e78b0dccc42783a5fc","tid":2432211,"uid":275498,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:55:36.000Z","msg":"on9 ,  cap 水 之後執笠"},{"pid":"65234979e0878395357dea726c827e8a9cd03630","tid":2432211,"uid":11512,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:56:29.000Z","msg":"Physical四分店被追租數次 涉款數百萬元<br />\n<br />\n舒適堡健身瑜珈中心屯門大興花園分店，於今年1月14日，被業主恒隆地產入稟，追討一個月、近35萬元租金。翻查紀錄，屯門分店於2020年5月、8月及12月，亦曾被業主入稟追租。<br />\n<br />\n除屯門分店外，舒適堡健身中心的康怡、長沙灣及上水分店，亦曾於去年5月、8月及9月被入稟追租，當中長沙灣分店於5月及8月，分別被追討三個月及兩個月租金，所涉總金額近200萬元。另外，康怡分店於5月 ，亦被業主恒隆地產入稟追討180萬元租金。"},{"pid":"2e6615b4cd5204f05ee1e2b58ab50cc9806c5e5c","tid":2432211,"uid":381174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"27c3bd6baa87ba3a4da0e0e78b0dccc42783a5fc","tid":2432211,"uid":275498,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:55:36.000Z","msg":"on9 ,  cap 水 之後執笠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:57:23.000Z","msg":"聽到心郁郁 但我都有咁嘅顧慮 所以睇下有冇ching join左分享下咩境環"},{"pid":"e400228f14834db2c4bd0cc48a964e4278861df6","tid":2432211,"uid":304321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:58:09.000Z","msg":"唔敢再續 本身今年年中完<br />\n武肺之下佢依家要去到年尾先完 到時再算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0037cf00216b98e75dc9e453c12eb4e383308bcb","tid":2432211,"uid":111460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:59:21.000Z","msg":"有無女教練幫我拉根？"},{"pid":"6a35c45817b99a5f4